All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AccountCreator
Class for creating accounts using names of types It can create "Credit", "Debit" and "Deposit" accounts
AccountException
Class of exceptions that uses in account class
Address
Model of address, contain city, street, house and number of flat, their getters and validator
Bank
Class for banks that have list of clients, id, accounts rate, and transfer functions
BankException
Class of exceptions that uses in bank and centralBank classes
BankTest
 
CentralBank
Class of central bank that used like main service
Client
Class for client of bank that have personal information and list of accounts
Client.ClientBuilder
Builder class with all parameters for client
ClientException
Class of exceptions that uses in client class
Clock
Class for virtual clock that contains getter for virtual time, functions for add and delete accounts that subscribed on this clock, function for skipping day and function for notify all subscribed accounts about new day
CreditAccount
Class of account that have not percent of income, but can have negative balance and have commission if it happened
CUI
 
DebitAccount
Class of account that have percent of income, but can not have negative balance
DepositAccount
Class of account that have percent of income that depends on balance, also it have time during which client can not withdraw money, it can not have negative balance
DepositInformation
Contains duration of unsafety status of deposit accounts and parts of deposit rate - intervals of amount of money and percents for them
DepositInformationPart
Class that have information about one interval of deposit rate
Email
Class that imitate email - it have address and list of input mails
IAccount
Interface for different types of account with getters for id and balance, with time skip function, updaters of time and rate, functions of add and reduce money
IAccountCreator
Interface for creating accounts using names of types
ICentralBank
Interface of central bank that used like main service
IClient
Interface for client of bank that have personal information and list of accounts
IClientBuilder
Builder interface for client with information that is not necessary
IClock
Interface for virtual clock that contains getter for virtual time, functions for add and delete accounts that subscribed on this clock, function for skipping day and function for notify all subscribed accounts about new day
IFirstnameBuilder
Builder interface for client with necessary firstname
ILastnameBuilder
Builder interface for client with necessary lastname
IRate
Interface that have all information of rates inside bank
Main
 
Passport
Model of passport, contain series and number, and validate check
Rate
Class that have all information of rates inside bank
RateException
Class of exceptions that uses in rate class
Transfer
Record that contains id and list of transfer parts It can give unmodifiable list of transfer parts
TransferPart
Record that contains bank and account ids, sum of operation and flag if it was deposit or withdraw
UI
 
VerifiedOperations
Class with methods that verified that operation can be done
